Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.08,0:00:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.86,0:00:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please keep the room bright \Nand sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.79,0:00:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.92,0:00:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's out training again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did say he would learn a \Nlethal technique this summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he seems to be feeling the pressure a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:23.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Namidabashi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.18,0:00:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he? An old boxer hitting 60?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I better work hard for Hinagiku, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.07,0:00:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right. For \NHinagiku, too... Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But his dedication is \Nwhat's so great about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is {\i1}not{\i0} great!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.53,0:00:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer break is about to end soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so shouldn't he want to spend more \Ntime with me {\i1}because{\i0} of that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.36,0:00:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should give a little thought to \Nhow Rocky felt when he lost Adrian!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! What in the world is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.48,0:00:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.92,0:01:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate Ayasaki has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea, Klaus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I thought that I should \Nnot let you be lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.81,0:01:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you came up with this plan to annoy me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.06,0:01:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.95,0:01:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Klaus, isn't your character \Ngrowing more and more distorted?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.79,0:01:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinda like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't mean that kind \Nof character distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I am not feeling lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am just a little bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh-ho! If you're that bored,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why not just take the plunge and \Nestablish an SOS Brigade or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.39,0:01:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be getting anime and \Nreality mixed up at your ripe old age.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being told such a thing by the Miss... \NI cannot go on living as a human being!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No helping it. I guess I'll \Nkill time by reading manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Study!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:47.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate the Combat Butler
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:52.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishing Lover Sanpei
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:56.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is one who serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:01:59.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is one who waits upon others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:03.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is a formal guardian,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:05.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who is there to support his mistress \Nin all aspects of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:07.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:11.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is about a boy who fights and puts \Nhis life on the line for a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:15.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A super combat battle story!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was it for my screen time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this was Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:28.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi ni kaketa bokura no yukue
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:28.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Our destination that we've \Nstaked upon this earth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:35.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuki-nukeru hayate no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:35.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sudden gale that cuts across
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Unmei ni makete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving in to fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:43.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shagami-komu nante tsumannai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:43.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And hunkering down is no fun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:47.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sore ja kakko warui yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:47.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:50.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uso kara deta makoto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:50.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Many a true word is spoken in jest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:56.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Koukai wa kitto mi kara deta sabi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:56.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Regret is probably reaping what you sowed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:59.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zettai, nase ba naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:59.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Where there's a will, \Nthere's definitely a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:06.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ooki na hamon ni nomi-komareteku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:06.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As a great rippling wave swallows us up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:12.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Karada nami ni makasereba
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:12.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it take you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:15.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kanchigai no yume
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:15.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams that are misguided
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:19.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mato-hazure no kitai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:19.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopes that are way off base
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:24.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuyoku omoeba itsuka tsukameru sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:24.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll grab them someday, \Nif you just have conviction
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:31.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi keri-age hashiri-dasou
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:31.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kick up the earth and start running
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:38.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimama ni mau kaze no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:38.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the capricious breeze that dances about
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Wonder Who Came Up with the Sound \NEffect 'Kapooon'. It's Awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The Miss said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was acting quite sulky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That summer break is almost over, but \Nyou aren't paying any attention to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.46,0:04:06.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been too distracted by the \Nissue of my lethal technique lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, so, what is she doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reading manga without studying, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall go keep her company right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, after she's read some manga, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishing Lover Sanpei
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...gets influenced by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go fishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:31.06,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(122,205)}Sanzenin\NSecret Base
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:31.06,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(289,134)}Sanzenin\NRacetrack
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:31.06,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(535,137)}Sanzenin\NResidence
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanzenin Lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:32.69,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(301,56)}Sanzenin\NLake
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(543,155)}Sanzenin\N Dome
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there other lakes as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's a tiny lake, though. \NAbout 2km in diameter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But can you really catch fish \Nin a lake on the property?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water comes from a spring, so it's clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also, her grandfather brought \Nfish from all over the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which have created a unique ecosystem,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:05:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so the lake is like its own little cosmos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to determine the dinner \Nmenu based on what you catch,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.52,0:05:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's a very convenient lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're the one doing the fishing, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, so we're self-sufficient when \Nit comes to fish dishes at this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.06,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(332,162)}Sanzenin\NLake
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.06,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(527,71)}Sanzenin\NPrivate Forest
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.06,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(543,155)}Sanzenin\N Dome
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! This is quite the lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is a nice, beautiful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we're going to fish like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we'll do fly fishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Fly fishing? Aren't we starting \Nwith something far too advanced?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanpei in "Fishing Lover Sanpei" \Nwas catching tons with fly fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Sanpei could do it, \Nthere's no way I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, it's not good to get \Nmanga and reality mixed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:43.60,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(75,128)}Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But well, this {\i1}is{\i0} an anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:43.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start with fishing using \Nsome kind of bait, like worms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishing using worms is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, instead of worms...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:05:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...how about some paste bait?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fishing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it begins with crucians \Nand ends with crucians.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:02.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Crucians = Crucian Carp
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, could it be that you intend \Nto fish as well, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I think I'll enjoy \Nfishing some crucian carp
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without having to think about \Ndinner ingredients for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That statement kind of muddles the issue
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as to whether the Sanzenin household \Nis actually impressive or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, paste bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just saw something huge in the lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? "Something"? Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably the guardian of \Nthis lake! No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria, is there such a thing in this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks so focused, I can't \Nbring myself to disturb her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.23,0:06:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More like, she's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, you just putter around \Nand catch some little fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.59,0:06:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch! {\i1}I{\i0} will go catch \Nthe guardian of this lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:06:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I think I'll use a lure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll need to watch the Miss, so she \Ndoesn't get tangled up in the line
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and get hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? Pop?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, the rod went flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous if you don't \Nhold on to it tightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got one! Yaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, quite a shapely crucian carp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You caught one already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I seem to have gotten one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Miss, this lake is really \Ngood for fishing for some reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see! Is that right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'll do it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishing is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got tired of it incredibly quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my rods go flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you don't hold on properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, it might be better \Nto take a boat out into the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all alone out here, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But fly fishing from a boat is difficult,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so perhaps it would be better to stay here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch closely. This is \Nhow you hold the rod and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, you can cast properly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:57.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}B-But I never imagined that \Nthe moment we were left alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:58.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that Hayate would sidle up to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's bolder than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:03.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's bound to fall off if she \Nswings a rod around on the boat,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:05.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I need to make sure I keep her steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose summer is almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot happened this summer, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like going to that seaside camp with everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and going to the amusement park with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-True...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had intended to come up with that lethal \Ntechnique during the summer break,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.97,0:09:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in the end, I was unable to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you were so kind \Nas to offer your assistance...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a good-for-nothing, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tha... That's not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we set off some sparklers \Ntogether after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little cute ones, like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But well, I hope we catch the \Nguardian of the lake before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't... really care if we \Ndon't catch him at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:09:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Miss! It's quite large! It just \Nmight be the guardian of the lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Watch out, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Hayate, where do \Nyou think you're grabbing me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, let go of the rod!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who should let go, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really shouldn't have pushed your limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're tiny, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Hinagiku's about the same size, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's quickly collect \NMaria and go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fishing, it begins with \Ncrucians and ends with crucians.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the guardian...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how did you catch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is classified information.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:39.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Incidentally, they apparently released \Nit because they couldn't eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, it's all about the crucians.\N({\u1}Da{\u0}kara hera dattsuuno, he{\u1}ra{\u0}.)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky Cha Cha Cha! No, wrong!\N({\u1}Ra{\u0}kkii cha cha cha! Ja na{\u1}i{\u0}!)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:12:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, you need to get out of \Nthose wet clothes quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! This all happened \Nbecause of you, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should both take a bath \Nbefore you catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You idiot! Take a bath \Ntogether with Hayate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I could do such \Nan embarrassing thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one said anything about \Nbathing together with Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do? I've made the Miss angry again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Hayate, you, too. \NDon't be so depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get warmed up quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um... When you say, \N"Let's get warmed up"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.76,0:12:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you're inviting \Nme to bathe with you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, like that would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I act in a way that \Nseemed like I was rejecting him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:57.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It sounds like there was yet \Nanother episode between these two
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:58.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that was open to misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baths are great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the crowning achievement of the \Ncivilization that the Lilim created.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monopolizing this enormous \Nbath all by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel all the little \Nmistakes floating away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, it'd be even better if \NI could enjoy this with Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maria, this is so...  bold...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go to such extremes to \Navoid temporary contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you afraid of connecting \Nwith other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.84,0:13:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:13:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how've you been lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How have I been? Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, don't you think the \Nwater's a bit lukewarm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You think so? Isn't this about normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crazy?! This is totally lukewarm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water's got to be {\i1}hot{\i0} for us Edoites!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:13.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,(Water-resistant)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Push.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you mess around with that stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:31.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty DANGEROUS, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.14,0:14:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I take this and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It's hard to press with my paw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You shouldn't be so rough with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that noise just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just heard a really loud noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're planning on running \Naway by yourself, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:14:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.01,0:15:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, what in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to use this for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:23.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I should apologize \Nto Hayate, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And tell him I feel bad for acting \Ncold towards him earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all people, to be seen \Nlike that by Maria...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go on living at \Nthis residence any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:15:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought Hayate would \Nget that depressed over me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, our love will come \Nto an end along with the summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do something about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there, butler-in-debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you so down about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, you're still \Nyoung. Don't brood so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose fault do you think this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how's about making up for it by dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there something I could \Ndo before I consider death?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start by fixing the bath \Nyou broke along with the boiler.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, but you're the \None who broke everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:46.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Boiler Room\NCaution: It's flammable, ya know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sanzenin residence \Nboiler is powered by AKIRA?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:17:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}this{\i0} mansion's boiler. \NIt's no ordinary beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or more like,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see markings that clearly indicate \Nmessing with things will be a bad idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with things here, \Namateur. It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want a tiger telling me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, are you really sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit your grumbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Meow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate! And Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um, I thought I'd \Nfix the bath that I broke,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I came down to the boiler room...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, what are {\i1}you{\i0} doing here, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.15,0:17:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had the same thought \Nas you to fix the bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:43.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She turned away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:47.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is terrible! She probably doesn't \Neven want to see my face anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Somehow, I feel awkward seeing him \Nafter that episode in the bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What are you crying about, Hayate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:18:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... Because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.25,0:18:03.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aw, man, this is kind of \Nbecoming a pain in the butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:05.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No guy should bawl like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:07.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the boiler, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:09.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll fix this and get on out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:13.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:15.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:16.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's so hard to press with my paw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Maria?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to drown at this \Nrate, so I'll drain the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! But how?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to borrow this for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I put a small crack in the wall, \Nthe water pressure should do the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll ride that wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on to me tightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boiler room is a mess now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:50.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks Set for Slightly Good Kids
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate?! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:20:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, this is about all I \Ncan do to return his feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but someday, for sure...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am a good-for-nothing, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always making trouble for others...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm not suited to \Nbeing a butler, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're capable of doing anything flawlessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're unable to do anything \Npassably without making mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the way you dedicate \Nyourself to these things...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it's not appealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.06,0:20:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll continue to work hard to \Nbe worthy of your kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But well, please do fix the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will! Let me get right to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it doesn't have to be now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maria...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha-ya-te!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.73,0:21:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you would go for Maria \Nwhen you already have me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You despicable scoundrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:38.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And thus, the butler-in-debt's \Nfond summer memories
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:41.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}met an untimely demise in the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:43.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So anyway, next episode, we finally \Nenter the new school term.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:45.70,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He will be fighting the \Nstudent council members
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as well as the teachers' conspiracies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.27,0:21:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good show!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:22:00.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Naida kokoro no ho ni kaze ga fuki-nuketetta
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:22:00.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A breeze crossed the wilted sail of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:05.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimochi yureru soshite Lose My Way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:05.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings waver and then I lose my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:08.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zutto kimi ga iru nara ii ka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:08.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess if you'll always be here, it's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.72,0:22:13.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sore mo waruku wa nai So I Go Together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.72,0:22:13.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not so bad, so I go together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:16.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tenki-yohou nante nai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:16.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Weather forecasts don't exist
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:19.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zenbu kibun-shidai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:19.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all mood-dependent
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.23,0:22:21.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nanimo shinpai nai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.23,0:22:21.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:24.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Makasete! Jiyuu-jizai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:24.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me! Perfectly free
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:26.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Keri-ageta kutsu ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:26.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,On the shoe that I kick up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:29.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Put A Wish" Zettai hareru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:29.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Put a Wish" it'll definitely clear up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.61,0:22:32.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kekka wa... I'm Looking At Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.61,0:22:32.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And the result is, I'm looking at nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:34.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mou ichido, yari-naoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:34.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time, a do-over!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:38.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tama ni wa kakete-miyou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:38.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try betting once in a while
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:42.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nee kimi ni yudanete-mitai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:42.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I want to try entrusting you with it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:47.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sassou to kake-nukete To Fly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:47.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Running through gallantly, to fly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.67,0:22:49.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Harema ga mieru The Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.67,0:22:49.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see a break in the weather, the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.13,0:22:51.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shinjiteta yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.13,0:22:51.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I had faith
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:54.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Soshite Make My Way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:54.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I make my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:22:57.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sotto sashi-dasu kimi no te de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:22:57.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With the hand you quietly reach out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.93,0:23:02.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Muteki ni nareru kara So I Go Together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.93,0:23:02.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I can become invincible, so I go together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.23,0:23:10.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hoshi ga kirei da ashita mo hareru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.23,0:23:10.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stars so beautiful, it'll \Nbe clear again tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Isumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.49,0:23:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Hayate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:31.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.44,0:23:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.45,0:23:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A good morning to yogurt! I'm Nagi Sanzenin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.05,0:23:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.41,0:23:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Isumi Saginomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi, this song is so soothing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my dear Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.38,0:23:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, you said the same \Nthing to Maria, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.68,0:23:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.65,0:23:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serving as a main host in this \Nsegment is too much for you, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.74,0:23:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.07,0:23:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You both seem to having such fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.21,0:23:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Sakuya will be \Nappearing starting next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.86,0:23:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fare-well-pickled scallions!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.39,0:23:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,240)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.34,0:23:58.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.36,0:24:01.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Makimura and I'll be in charge \Nof this class starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.39,0:24:19.42,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of "Hayate \Nthe Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.55,0:24:04.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's the developer of \Nthe caregiver robot doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.54,0:24:06.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. At this rate, \Nmy position at Hakuou...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.62,0:24:09.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,No, my position in this very \Nanime is extremely precarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.35,0:24:11.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,So there you have it, Ayasaki! \NYou're going to help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.47,0:24:12.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.57,0:24:14.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.28,0:24:16.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Non-Kiddy Genius Teacher Appears".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.51,0:24:18.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get depressed, Hayata!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.48,0:24:22.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, how do I say this? \NI like being punished, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.42,0:24:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Non-Kiddy Genius Teacher Appears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.44,0:24:24.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Can {\i1}you{\i0} believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.86,0:24:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
